L7 APPLICATION
├── HTTP, FTP, SMTP, DNS, SSH
└── End-user services

L6 PRESENTATION
├── Encryption (SSL/TLS)
└── Data formatting

L5 SESSION
└── Session handling

L4 TRANSPORT
├── TCP
└── UDP

   ICMP(L3)
    ↓
    Lives between L3-L4
    ├── Error reporting
    ├── Network diagnostics
    └── Ping/traceroute

L3 NETWORK
├── IP (IPv4, IPv6)
└── Routing

L2 DATA LINK
├── MAC addresses
└── Ethernet frames

L1 PHYSICAL
└── Raw bits/signals

////////////////////

DATA ENCAPSULATION

[L7] Application Data
  ↓
[L6] + Presentation Info
  ↓
[L5] + Session Info
  ↓
[L4] + TCP/UDP Header
  ↓
[L3] + IP Header
  ↓
[L2] + MAC Header/Trailer
  ↓
[L1] = Bits